  → Linux/fhs/lib/ld-linux-so-2
  -
  → Linux/fhs/lib/firmware
  -
  → Linux/fhs/lib/lsb
  -
  → Linux/fhs/lib/modules
  -
  → Linux/fhs/lib/udev

  → Linux/fhs/usr/lib

  → Linux/fhs/lib/firmware/index

  → Linux/fhs/lib/lsb/index

  → development/dynamic-loader

  → https://refspecs.linuxfoundation.org/FHS_3.0/fhs/ch03s09.html
